Steps for any wallet setup :-

1. Download and install wallet from genuine sources or official website.

2. Backup of 8-12 word Phrase or QR code

3. Wallet is ready to use

4. Set Pin or Password for spending from settings

5. Share only the address to send or receive funds.

1. Hamesha official website ya genuine source se hi wallet download karein.
2. Apne 8-12 word phrase (seed phrase) ya QR code ka backup zaroor lein.
3. Wallet ready hone ke baad, spending ke liye ek Pin ya Password set karein.
4. Kisi ko bhi apni private details na dein, pin jaise upi m et krte h,waise hi bina pin k aap kie ko v crypto ni bhej paoge.
5. sirf Address share karein funds mangwane ke liye.
